1144
01:17:27.356 --> 01:17:28.524
Good. Don't plop.

1145
01:17:29.066 --> 01:17:31.235
No jolts. Good.

1146
01:17:33.195 --> 01:17:34.196
I'm okay.

1147
01:17:35.989 --> 01:17:37.824
- I just wanna feel better.
